      jargon-heavy — /seeit is for a non-technical person to SEE+FEEL governed behavior, not follow dev
      commands (= editorial Risk #1). Building the surface is not enough; it must pass the accessibility
      bar.'
    bar: 'ACCESSIBLE AND GROUNDED (the intersection): plain-language-first · dev command available-not-required
