    rail_position: 'STANDING publish-gate, ALL series/volumes: after the seeit build (seeit_figures) +
      before publish — the /seeit analog of the manuscript editorial+Tech/Arch boards. A volume is NOT
      publish-ready until its /seeit pages are accessible-grounded:PASS (all 4 personas + cold-reader
